StructureDefinition-CareConnect-MedicationAdministration-1

Describes the event of a patient consuming or otherwise being administered a medication.

Profile Minimum Viable Content (MVC)

The following elements are mandatory in the FHIR profile (i.e. MUST be present):

  1. status
  2. medicationReference
  3. subject
  4. effective[x]

Examples

  • CareConnect-MedicationAdministration-1 Example
